\c 36
\s Kuipa kwoakaipa nokunaka kwaMwari
\d Kumutungamiriri wokuimba. Pisarema raDhavhidhi muranda wafehovha.
\p
\v 1 Kudarika kwoakaipa kunoreva mumwoyo mangu, kuchiti, "Hakuna kutya Mwari pamberi pameso ake."
\v 2 Nokuti anozvibata kumeso kwake, Achiti zvakaipa zvake hazvingazikanwi zvikavengwa.
\v 3 Mashoko omuromo wake ndizvo zvakaipa nokunyengera; Akarega kuzova akachenjera nokuita zvakanaka.
\v 4 Anofunga zvakaipa panhoo dzake; Anofamba nenzira isina kunaka; Haasemi zvakaipa.
\v 5 Unyoro hwenyu, Jehovha, hwakasvika kudenga-denga; Kutendeka kwenyu kunosvikira kumakore;
\v 6 Kururama kwenyu kwakafanana namakomo aMwari; Kutonga kwenyu kwakadzika zvikuru; Jehovha, munochengeta vanhu nemhuka.
\v 7 Unyoro hwenyu, Mwari, hwakanaka-naka sei! Vana vavanhu vanondovanda pasi pomumvuri wamapapiro enyu.
\v 8 Vachagutswa kwazvo nezvakakora zveimba yenyu; Muchavanwisa parwizi rwezvinofadza zvenyu;
\v 9 Nokuti kwamuri ndiko kune tsime roupenyu; Muchiedza chenyu ndimo matinoona chiedza. mucVitira vanokuzivai unyoro hwcnyu;
\s Nokururama kwenyu kuna
\s vamwoyo yakarurama.
\s ll Rutsoka rwoanozvikudza ngarurege
\s kusvikira kwandiri,
\s Ruoko rwoakaipa ngarurege kundidzinga.
\p
\v 12 Apo ndopakawira pasi vaiti vezvakaipa,
\s Vakawisirwa pasi, havangagoni kumuk azve.
